OL,4,C'Reckless' to scrap BTecs, educators
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,6, BTec qualifications should not be
OL,7, scrapped in England, say groups
OL,8, representing students and staff in
OL,9, schools, colleges and universities.
OL,11,FThe plea comes as the Department for
OL,12,FEducation confirmed plans to introduce
OL,13,Fnew technical qualifications in England
OL,14,Fand scrap most BTecs.
OL,16,FThe department says the reforms will
OL,17,Fsimplify and streamline the system.
OL,19,FBut education leaders warn getting rid
OL,20,Fof BTecs is "reckless", as it will harm
OL,21,Fthe prospects of poorer pupils.
